high_descs: Turn around and head to the kitchen on the right to reach the countertop.
Pick up the ladle from the counter.
Turn right to reach the sink.
Wash the ladle in the sink and take it out.
Turn right and head to the cabinet on the left.
Put the ladle in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed ladle in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around go straight turn left then turn right to the countertop in the kitchen.
Place the ladle from the counter top.
Turn around then turn left to the sink.
Put the ladle in the sink, pour the water and take it back.
Turn right go straight then turn right to the cabinet.
Place the ladle in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place the ladle from the counter top clean it and Place it in the cabinet

high_descs: Take the Cooking utensil in the counter top
Put the Cooking utensil in the sink, clean it off
Take back in the Cooking utensil
Place the Cooking utensil on the cabinet
anns.task_desc: Take the Cooking utensil in the counter top  Place the Cooking utensil on the cabinet
